    <item>
      <title>随着人工智能需求飙升，NextEra 采取措施重启核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/nextera-takes-step-to-restart-nuclear-plant-as-ai-demand-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NextEra Energy Inc. 已请求美国监管机构更改其已关闭的杜安阿诺德核电站的许可证，这是在人工智能和数据中心电力消耗飙升的情况下重启爱荷华州核电站的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/nextera-takes-step-to-restart-nuclear-plant-as-ai-demand-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新版全球外汇法规发布 重点关注透明度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/revised-global-fx-code-released-with-focus-on-transparency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责监督每日交易量 7.5 万亿美元的外汇市场自愿最佳实践准则的委员会修改了指导方针，以提高这个监管松散的行业的透明度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/revised-global-fx-code-released-with-focus-on-transparency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行明确加息指引安抚市场但可能适得其反</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/boj-s-clear-guidance-on-rate-hike-calms-markets-but-may-backfire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田和夫将利率提高至 2008 年以来的最高水平，通过谨慎地向投资者传达他的计划，避免了市场动荡。但这一策略本身也存在风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/boj-s-clear-guidance-on-rate-hike-calms-markets-but-may-backfire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
